OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and dry start to the
OL,6,Fday, although the cloud will soon thin
OL,7,Fand break to give warm sunny spells
OL,8,Finto the afternoon. Winds generally
OL,9,Flight, breezy along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry with variable
OL,12,Fcloud and clear spells. The odd mist
OL,13,For fog patch is possible in some rural
OL,14,Fspots. Generally a warm night, with
OL,15,Flight winds. Breezy along coasts.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FStaying fine and dry, with
OL,18,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells
OL,19,Fthroughout the day. Feeling warm in
OL,20,Fthe sunshine, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
